data.value: The Hotnitsa eco-trail is located in the Veliko Tarnovo area, near the village of Hotnitsa. It is built along the gorge of the Bohoth River. The ecopath starts with a beautiful waterfall with a height of about 30 m and a small pond. A distinctive feature of waterfalls is their specific greenish color. A suitable place for picnics.
